content.rendered:
Directed by Sachin P. Karande

Written by Sanjeev Dutta

Cast Amit Sadh (Detective). Arbaaz Khan (Walia). Sonal Chauhan (Shilpa). Evelyn Sharma (Lara). Rajdeep Choudhury (Mystery Man).Sudip Sarangi. Sachin Parikh (Translator) . Joy Badlani (Sharma). Rajat Ajay Bose (The Handsome Guy). Rajeev Mehra

Language Hindi

Producers Rohit Hansraj. SudhaNshu Kumar. Sagar Sinagare. Vishal Singh. Yogesh Singh

Production Balcony Film
